---
title: Dashboard UI Implementation
requires: [Vue3, Tailwind]
---

# Dashboard UI Implementation

## Objective
Build the dynamic visual interface to list Totem instances and view their details.

## Tasks
1. Build `InstanceList.vue` - a modern, stylized sidebar/grid displaying all available instances globally.
2. Build `InstanceDetail.vue` - a main content area displaying the README.md transformed to HTML or formatted markdown.
3. Add subtle hover micro-animations and a premium dark-mode aesthetic.
4. Integrate the `useInstances` composable to display real data.
